# arthurs-portfolio — Cursor Rules

## General
- Keep it simple — no over-engineering for a portfolio site
- Named exports preferred over default exports (except Next.js `page.tsx` / `layout.tsx`)
- No `any` type — use proper TypeScript types
- TailwindCSS utility classes only — no custom CSS unless clearly necessary

## Naming
- Components: PascalCase (`HeroSection.tsx` → `export function HeroSection`)
- Utils: camelCase or kebab-case files
- Constants: `UPPER_SNAKE_CASE`

See `README.md` for project overview.
